name: Thison’s creation #2 “ NATURE VS NURTURE ”
description:
A regular dude chilling in nature but there is a profound meaning behind this artwork. It's all about mangrove conservation. The importance of preserving the environment for a sustainable biodiversity and the fact that we are in debt to nature for all its amazing gifts.

Original concept and digital illustration by Thison Nayanake from Ceylon Metaverse. Copyright ownership is granted to token holders. Collectors can tag us on Twitter @CeylonMetaverse and/ or message us so we can grant you a letter of authenticity.
